latestPosts.caption:
It all started when @tusharkhurana433 and I dared to dream big and thought that together we can possibly create an iconic brand (which is now called @perforaofficial) and positively impact and improve the oral hygiene of millions of Indian consumers.

This fundraise is a very important step in our journey as it gives us a chance to create innovative, effective and safe products, build distribution and amplify our awareness amongst the Indian audience.

We are extremely grateful and privileged to have the support of possibly the best consumer brand investors - @sauce_vc (investors in @xyxxcrew @thewholetruthfoods, etc.), @manuchandra1, @kvk237 @sambit.dash.33, @hershgulati, @rpsggroup (investors in @thesouledstore, @mcaffeineofficial, etc.) who believe in our vision and execution capabilities.

Building a business/brand is a tough task and raising capital is an important but only one part of the bigger goal. There is so much that goes behind fundraising and to be candid, it is a tedious process however if you have the right investors on board, it gets relatively easier. 

Thank you so much everyone who texted / called me to congratulate and has been a part of our journey. 

Congratulations to everyone in the team @perforaofficial. These guys are the ones who are working tirelessly to create an exceptional experience and in the process helping us realise our dream. Truly grateful 🙏.

After 30+ months of conceptualising the idea, it is finally starting to feel like we are living the dream. 

Back to work now because a lot needs to be done :)

#dreams #fundraising #d2c #entrepreneur #perfora

latestPosts.caption:
Some called it magic, others called it fake 👀 

But guess what? We listened.
We’re saying goodbye to the old Purple Serum...
To bring you something better, more effective and even more purple 💜

The new serum is out now for you to try! Shop yours now ⚡
.
(Purple Serum, Teeth Whitening, Teeth, Perfora, trending reels, explore, dentist, clean teeth, yellow teeth, yellow teeth to white teeth, how to clean teeth yellow to white, teeth reels, teeth cleaning)

(#teethwhiteningathome #teethwhitenathome #teethwhitening #teethwhiteningservices #yellowteeth #cleanteeth #teethcleaning #purpleserum #trendingreels #teethwhitener)

In August 2023, we launched a game changing product i.e. Purple Magic Whitening Serum, a product that helps in reducing yellow teeth stains, powered by color theory. Purple neutralises yellow implying when you apply purple color on yellow teeth, it will make the yellow color lighter and teeth whiter.

Over the last 12 months, after witnessing some early signs of customer love and validation, we reworked the product formulation to make it even more effective and also got In Vivo clinical trials done to build even more conviction on product efficacy.

There are people who call this product fake or end up saying this purple serum is gimmicky and doesn’t work. Well, we understand their feedback and take into our consideration however I want to say that sometimes it will take longer to show results and sometimes it is more instant. The results completely depend on product application, current color state of teeth and time duration of the product usage.

I use this product every single day, once a day and I can confidently say this product is effective. I drink 5 cups of black coffee every day and my teeth have very minimal yellow stains.

If you haven’t tried the Perfora Purple Magic Serum, I believe you should give it a try and experience the magic of color theory.

Special thanks to @dontcallmekanye for the voiceover and the execution. Grateful to have such a solid team in place.

#purple #purpleserum #colortheory #entrepreneurship
